{"tid":736014,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"以商業角度計，香港應該好多人希望英格蘭入到世界盃決賽","createTime":"2018-07-10T02:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T09:08:27.000Z","uid":36494,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"26580a2e66bd7656136e1593309eb365f08475ea","tid":736014,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"計收視英格蘭入決賽一定高過克羅地亞入決賽，電視台同廣告商都開心<br />\n<br />\n酒吧生意又好啲<br />\n<br />\n蘋果又可以拎嚟做頭條新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔理商業考慮<br />\n一般球迷對英格蘭球員亦熟悉多啲，睇決賽都投入多啲<br />\n港女被人問起決賽支持邊隊，起碼識得答「我支持英格蘭，因為碧咸好靚仔」"},{"pid":"474e0bb31043c68e6eadd125999500dda389c479","tid":736014,"uid":41434,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"已家7號都唔差 同碧咸一樣都有手有腳"},{"pid":"370e4184950c8f9ac4abf708b3a6c9fa9a567c1e","tid":736014,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"所以我地應該反主流<br />\n支持格仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e243c3ce54771e2e12b0add1537fe817b41349","tid":736014,"uid":194120,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"啲夜場生意朋友話如果France vs England啲人第朝返工都會出嚟睇.<br />\nBelgium vs Croatia就一定差啲."},{"pid":"a19f94f8ed91d5ef1f3710075fbfe139e1835253","tid":736014,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"決賽有英格蘭，viu收視又好啲<br />\n想睇 Cctvb 喊咁口"},{"pid":"208971ec54650ed275a5a427395d4c66279c1e1b","tid":736014,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92e243c3ce54771e2e12b0add1537fe817b41349","tid":736014,"uid":194120,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"啲夜場生意朋友話如果France vs England啲人第朝返工都會出嚟睇.<br />\nBelgium vs Croatia就一定差啲."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:02:19.000Z","msg":"Belgium vs England 呢咁?"},{"pid":"61945623182312c329c6e91f085eaf8ff89eb404","tid":736014,"uid":158411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"rep